WEBVTT

00:00:42.520 --> 00:00:43.159
Senior Sister, Senior Sister

00:00:44.159 --> 00:00:45.159
Fang Jie, you're back.

00:00:45.159 --> 00:00:45.640
Senior Sister.

00:00:46.399 --> 00:00:46.880
Fangfang.

00:00:47.679 --> 00:00:48.439
Senior Sister, Senior Sister.

00:00:48.679 --> 00:00:49.200
Senior Sister.

00:00:50.640 --> 00:00:51.079
Senior Sister.

00:00:52.240 --> 00:00:52.719
Senior Sister.

00:01:22.159 --> 00:01:23.680
Working so hard as soon as you get back?

00:01:26.400 --> 00:01:27.200
Not bad.

00:01:28.319 --> 00:01:29.120
You're already studying

00:01:29.120 --> 00:01:30.719
the experiment plan for next semester.

00:01:33.439 --> 00:01:35.079
Getting ahead creates a virtuous cycle.

00:01:35.879 --> 00:01:36.799
No, but this plant of yours...

00:01:36.799 --> 00:01:39.280
needs at least three more cultivations to show traits.

00:01:39.439 --> 00:01:41.040
You just need to record it after each harvest.

00:01:41.519 --> 00:01:42.760
No need to be this far ahead.

00:01:43.079 --> 00:01:45.079
Next semester's procurement list.

00:01:45.159 --> 00:01:46.719
Year-end safety inspection procedures.

00:01:46.920 --> 00:01:49.640
Thirty-six snacks everyone loves. You...

00:01:50.239 --> 00:01:51.799
You're not planning to drop out, are you?

00:01:58.159 --> 00:01:58.879
You're dropping out?

00:02:05.079 --> 00:02:05.560
Gui Fang.

00:02:06.640 --> 00:02:08.280
Our department has a quota for the direct Ph.D. program every year.

00:02:08.919 --> 00:02:09.960
You'll be a senior next semester.

00:02:09.960 --> 00:02:10.919
I intend to recommend you.

00:02:13.360 --> 00:02:14.159
No need, Professor.

00:02:14.800 --> 00:02:16.840
It would be a waste to give that spot to me.

00:02:16.919 --> 00:02:18.000
You're not doing research anymore?

00:02:23.520 --> 00:02:25.319
Gui Fang, in farming practice...

00:02:25.800 --> 00:02:27.240
you are the most talented student

00:02:27.520 --> 00:02:28.599
I have seen in years.

00:02:34.080 --> 00:02:34.800
I really don't need it.

00:02:37.039 --> 00:02:38.080
I might...

00:02:41.120 --> 00:02:42.439
need to take a long leave.

00:02:49.840 --> 00:02:50.639
Think it over.

00:02:53.120 --> 00:02:54.000
Don't be in a hurry to refuse.

00:03:50.919 --> 00:03:53.000
Doing it is what takes courage.

00:03:54.759 --> 00:03:56.639
Student Gui Fang found the difference.

00:03:56.879 --> 00:03:57.599
Quite talented.

00:03:57.599 --> 00:03:59.560
Gui Fang, can you teach me how to draw the rhizomes?

00:03:59.639 --> 00:04:01.400
Your raw sketches are so beautiful.

00:04:01.800 --> 00:04:03.120
The regrets of being in your twenties

00:04:03.479 --> 00:04:05.319
can be fulfilled when you're nearly fifty.

00:04:05.400 --> 00:04:06.520
I don't accept reconciliation.

00:04:06.599 --> 00:04:08.159
That's amazing.

00:04:08.960 --> 00:04:10.199
Those researchers...

00:04:10.400 --> 00:04:11.639
are exactly what I want to become.

00:04:11.840 --> 00:04:13.840
That is the life I want to pursue.

00:04:38.120 --> 00:04:38.639
Oh my god.

00:04:40.319 --> 00:04:41.040
This still works.

00:04:41.439 --> 00:04:42.319
It's a pity to throw it away.

00:04:42.480 --> 00:04:43.800
What? You want to pick it up and take it back?

00:04:46.120 --> 00:04:46.720
Brother Xiao Can.

00:04:48.680 --> 00:04:49.160
Stop right there.

00:04:49.720 --> 00:04:51.639
Let's not do that melodramatic romance drama stuff.

00:04:51.879 --> 00:04:53.439
I have no last wishes for you to inherit.

00:04:53.519 --> 00:04:55.399
And certainly no inheritance for you to distribute.

00:04:55.519 --> 00:04:56.839
I don't need you to be happy for me.

00:04:57.040 --> 00:04:58.000
I have important family members...

00:04:58.000 --> 00:04:59.600
but I don't need you to take care of them for me.

00:05:01.439 --> 00:05:01.800
Tian'er.

00:05:02.519 --> 00:05:05.439
I hope you stay handsome and beautiful on your own.

00:05:25.160 --> 00:05:25.639
Come on.

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:29.519
Buddy.

00:05:29.839 --> 00:05:30.240
Buddy.

00:05:30.959 --> 00:05:31.800
What about the computer?

00:05:32.480 --> 00:05:33.519
Won't sell for much. I'll give it to you.

00:05:35.040 --> 00:05:36.480
These shoes of yours are nice.

00:05:36.839 --> 00:05:37.600
Those are worth even less.

00:05:37.600 --> 00:05:38.160
Take them all.

00:05:38.399 --> 00:05:39.680
You haven't even used these toiletries.

00:05:39.879 --> 00:05:40.279
Take them.

00:05:40.759 --> 00:05:41.120
Take it all.

00:05:41.600 --> 00:05:44.040
This curtain seems to suit me quite well.

00:05:44.160 --> 00:05:44.560
Take it.

00:05:44.920 --> 00:05:45.800
Use it as a tablecloth.

00:05:45.800 --> 00:05:47.040
Or turn it into a skirt or something.

00:05:47.519 --> 00:05:48.199
I'm a student.

00:05:48.399 --> 00:05:48.920
Give me free shipping.

00:05:49.199 --> 00:05:49.560
Sure.

00:05:49.959 --> 00:05:50.639
I'm a pampered wife.

00:05:50.639 --> 00:05:51.600
Give it to me for free.

00:05:52.920 --> 00:05:54.759
Brother Xiao Can, what about these clothes?

00:05:54.920 --> 00:05:55.959
Just wear them as pajamas.

00:06:28.240 --> 00:06:30.720
This was a gift for Sister Rui, right?

00:06:34.879 --> 00:06:35.680
What did you leave for her?

00:06:37.480 --> 00:06:38.079
Nothing at all.

00:06:39.480 --> 00:06:40.519
In her life from now on...

00:06:40.839 --> 00:06:42.079
it's best if there are no traces of me.

00:06:46.279 --> 00:06:46.680
Buddy.

00:06:47.639 --> 00:06:48.160
How about...

00:06:49.079 --> 00:06:50.600
we hold a living funeral for you?

00:06:53.199 --> 00:06:53.920
What's with you?

00:06:54.240 --> 00:06:55.959
You think my mom and Xu Rui aren't sad enough?

00:07:00.639 --> 00:07:01.560
Leave them alone.

00:07:01.959 --> 00:07:03.000
Once is painful enough.

00:07:06.480 --> 00:07:07.519
Then... then...

00:07:08.120 --> 00:07:10.360
Do you have any unfulfilled wishes?

00:07:13.360 --> 00:07:15.680
If I really have to think of one...

00:07:28.759 --> 00:07:29.399
Xiaocan

00:07:30.360 --> 00:07:30.879
Don't think about it

00:07:31.680 --> 00:07:32.920
Why have a wedding when I'm dying?

00:07:32.920 --> 00:07:34.319
Wouldn't that just burden someone for life?

00:07:35.279 --> 00:07:35.759
No

00:07:36.360 --> 00:07:37.560
I think it's been a perfect life

00:07:38.600 --> 00:07:39.040
Brilliant

00:07:40.439 --> 00:07:42.079
But if you insist on asking

00:07:42.879 --> 00:07:43.759
There is one thing

00:07:43.920 --> 00:07:44.319
Tell me

00:07:44.639 --> 00:07:45.360
I wish

00:07:45.519 --> 00:07:46.800
That my brilliant life

00:07:47.040 --> 00:07:49.240
Would end in a dazzling display of fireworks

00:07:50.399 --> 00:07:51.439
Fireworks. Okay

00:07:52.000 --> 00:07:52.480
I'll figure something out

00:07:52.480 --> 00:07:54.000
If you force me to think of another

00:07:54.120 --> 00:07:54.759
There is one more

00:07:54.879 --> 00:07:55.519
Tell me, tell me

00:07:55.639 --> 00:07:56.480
I want to beat you up

00:07:57.040 --> 00:07:58.040
A really solid one

00:07:59.720 --> 00:08:00.319
You can only choose one

00:08:00.319 --> 00:08:01.079
Then I'll choose the second one

00:08:02.079 --> 00:08:03.240
Choosing one means

00:08:03.720 --> 00:08:04.600
You can only choose the first one

00:08:12.879 --> 00:08:14.600
I didn't expect to leave tomorrow

00:08:14.959 --> 00:08:16.240
It's really quite emotional

00:08:19.240 --> 00:08:20.160
Changed to tomorrow again?

00:08:20.160 --> 00:08:21.519
Moved up? Wasn't it the day after tomorrow?

00:08:21.839 --> 00:08:22.519
Tomorrow

00:08:23.439 --> 00:08:24.000
Who said that?

00:08:24.240 --> 00:08:25.079
The driver said so

00:08:25.600 --> 00:08:26.360
Which driver?

00:08:27.399 --> 00:08:28.600
The truck driver

00:08:28.600 --> 00:08:29.439
Who did you think I meant?

00:08:33.240 --> 00:08:34.840
I thought you got a master to calculate it for me

00:08:35.039 --> 00:08:35.960
You meant moving house?

00:08:37.200 --> 00:08:37.799
What else?

00:08:39.600 --> 00:08:40.399
I meant moving in

00:08:41.080 --> 00:08:41.519
It's the same day

00:08:42.960 --> 00:08:43.519
You scared me to death

00:08:46.279 --> 00:08:48.200
Auntie has lived here for over ten years

00:08:49.000 --> 00:08:52.600
I didn't expect her to leave with just a few boxes

00:08:54.000 --> 00:08:56.399
Didn't we rent a fully furnished place?

00:08:56.799 --> 00:08:58.039
Besides, that old furniture

00:08:58.159 --> 00:08:59.200
And old appliances can't be used either

00:08:59.759 --> 00:09:00.799
Once my mom settles down

00:09:00.799 --> 00:09:02.320
We'll get new ones when she buys a new place

00:09:03.080 --> 00:09:03.919
Do you feel that

00:09:03.919 --> 00:09:06.519
Auntie has been unusually calm lately

00:09:07.879 --> 00:09:09.240
Indeed

00:09:10.200 --> 00:09:11.919
Like when I suggested renting a place with a yard

00:09:12.399 --> 00:09:13.440
She signed without a word

00:09:14.039 --> 00:09:15.679
I said to throw away all the old furniture

00:09:15.919 --> 00:09:16.600
And she agreed

00:09:18.679 --> 00:09:19.200
Of course

00:09:20.120 --> 00:09:21.360
We can't really empathize

00:09:22.080 --> 00:09:23.519
After all, I've never lost a son

00:09:27.080 --> 00:09:27.679
Don't worry

00:09:28.519 --> 00:09:29.840
I'll stay with Auntie for a few days

00:09:32.600 --> 00:09:33.240
Just a few days?

00:09:34.159 --> 00:09:35.679
And then? You'll forget me?

00:09:36.120 --> 00:09:37.159
And throw yourself into someone else's arms?

00:09:38.039 --> 00:09:39.840
No way, I can't bear to part with you

00:09:39.879 --> 00:09:41.080
What else?

00:09:41.399 --> 00:09:43.080
You want me to go with you?

00:09:43.960 --> 00:09:44.639
Not go with me

00:09:45.039 --> 00:09:45.480
But wait

00:09:46.480 --> 00:09:47.559
I'll wait for you over there

00:09:48.320 --> 00:09:48.960
Don't worry

00:09:49.039 --> 00:09:50.279
With my social skills

00:09:50.279 --> 00:09:51.840
I'll definitely thrive over there

00:09:52.159 --> 00:09:53.240
When you get there

00:09:53.240 --> 00:09:54.480
You'll find you feel at home

00:09:54.639 --> 00:09:55.279
And brighten up the place

00:09:56.679 --> 00:09:59.600
Then when I talk to my future husband

00:09:59.600 --> 00:10:01.080
About my ex

00:10:01.440 --> 00:10:02.720
I'll have to ask if he minds

00:10:03.759 --> 00:10:04.960
Future husband

00:10:05.639 --> 00:10:06.360
Isn't that me?

00:10:20.279 --> 00:10:20.919
Xiaocan

00:10:24.960 --> 00:10:27.039
Then I'll wait for you two to come together

00:10:30.559 --> 00:10:31.919
I really don't want to go

00:10:32.000 --> 00:10:33.440
I really can't bear to leave you

00:10:40.120 --> 00:10:41.600
Fang'er, you made this soup base yourself, right?

00:10:42.159 --> 00:10:42.919
Smells so good.

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:44.039
Is it cooked?

00:10:44.240 --> 00:10:45.039
It's cooked, it's cooked.

00:10:45.039 --> 00:10:45.679
Eat this, have more of this.

00:10:45.679 --> 00:10:46.240
It's definitely ready to eat.

00:10:46.240 --> 00:10:47.279
Don't boil this for too long.

00:10:47.559 --> 00:10:48.399
I'm not bragging to you guys.

00:10:48.960 --> 00:10:50.279
But these duck intestines my Godmother makes...

00:10:50.480 --> 00:10:51.360
Are the best in the world.

00:10:51.440 --> 00:10:52.200
If she claims second place,

00:10:52.200 --> 00:10:52.960
No one dares claim first.

00:10:53.720 --> 00:10:54.679
Unlike our Xiao Yin.

00:10:55.360 --> 00:10:55.960
If she claims second place,

00:10:56.080 --> 00:10:57.000
Then everyone else is first.

00:10:57.960 --> 00:10:58.679
Li Wai.

00:10:59.000 --> 00:11:00.240
If it's tasty, just eat more.

00:11:00.480 --> 00:11:01.240
Godmother will...

00:11:01.240 --> 00:11:02.559
Send you the secret recipe later.

00:11:02.759 --> 00:11:05.240
No way, every chef has their own touch.

00:11:05.799 --> 00:11:06.919
I have to keep eating what Godmother makes.

00:11:09.440 --> 00:11:09.919
Gui Fang.

00:11:10.600 --> 00:11:12.679
You'll keep making this for us to eat, right?

00:11:17.320 --> 00:11:18.120
Why are you kicking me?

00:11:18.360 --> 00:11:19.120
What's wrong with kicking you?

00:11:20.759 --> 00:11:21.679
Come on, come on, let's eat.

00:11:21.919 --> 00:11:22.600
Eat more, have some meat, have some meat.

00:11:22.600 --> 00:11:23.000
Have some meat.

00:11:23.279 --> 00:11:24.639
Here, have some greens, have some greens.

00:11:25.399 --> 00:11:25.960
Come on, come on.

00:11:26.879 --> 00:11:27.919
Speaking of duck intestines...

00:11:28.240 --> 00:11:29.440
In the dorm upstairs from us,

00:11:29.639 --> 00:11:30.759
There's a senior whose duck...

00:11:30.759 --> 00:11:32.240
Ate the experimental field of the class next door.

00:11:32.799 --> 00:11:34.720
Now the whole class is blocking the dorm door,

00:11:34.919 --> 00:11:36.200
Demanding the duck involved be handed over.

00:11:36.320 --> 00:11:37.960
They want to kill the duck to vent their anger?

00:11:38.200 --> 00:11:38.879
No.

00:11:39.080 --> 00:11:39.480
They...

00:11:39.720 --> 00:11:41.720
Invited the duck involved to the lab.

00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:45.080
Then the whole class is taking turns on guard duty,

00:11:45.240 --> 00:11:46.519
Just staring at that duck,

00:11:47.320 --> 00:11:47.840
Waiting for it to...

00:11:48.440 --> 00:11:48.799
Poop the seeds out.

00:11:49.759 --> 00:11:50.759
So they really want to vent feces.

00:11:52.360 --> 00:11:53.000
We're eating here.

00:11:53.039 --> 00:11:53.679
We're eating!

00:11:53.679 --> 00:11:54.960
Why are you so disgusting?

00:11:54.960 --> 00:11:56.759
You guys mix fertilizer every day and still mind this?

00:11:57.279 --> 00:11:59.320
None of you actually like your major.

00:11:59.840 --> 00:12:00.559
It's all for survival.

00:12:00.799 --> 00:12:01.320
Gui Fang...

00:12:02.039 --> 00:12:02.840
Don't you guys think...

00:12:03.279 --> 00:12:04.639
Gui Fang is like Mother Earth?

00:12:05.000 --> 00:12:05.679
Loving life.

00:12:06.600 --> 00:12:07.120
My foot...

00:12:07.120 --> 00:12:08.120
Wei Mingtian.

00:12:11.360 --> 00:12:12.039
Hungry, right?

00:12:12.360 --> 00:12:13.799
Come on, eat more, eat more.

00:12:13.799 --> 00:12:15.200
Eat, have some meat.

00:12:15.200 --> 00:12:15.720
Here.

00:12:16.320 --> 00:12:17.039
Have some chicken heart.

00:12:17.279 --> 00:12:17.840
Grow some sense.

00:12:18.320 --> 00:12:19.559
Speaking of chicken hearts...

00:12:20.600 --> 00:12:21.399
Back in our hometown,

00:12:21.720 --> 00:12:22.639
Before eating a chicken heart,

00:12:22.639 --> 00:12:24.360
You have to let someone take a bite first.

00:12:24.679 --> 00:12:25.039
Why?

00:12:25.120 --> 00:12:25.639
Why?

00:12:26.000 --> 00:12:27.720
Because if you eat too many solid chicken hearts,

00:12:28.000 --> 00:12:29.159
You'll easily become hard-headed.

00:12:29.840 --> 00:12:30.639
You're really humorous.

00:12:30.840 --> 00:12:32.720
Then if you eat a chicken heart that's half-bitten,

00:12:32.840 --> 00:12:33.919
Wouldn't you become half-witted?

00:12:34.320 --> 00:12:34.840
Never heard of that.

00:12:36.759 --> 00:12:37.440
In my family,

00:12:37.759 --> 00:12:39.159
Chicken hearts are good stuff.

00:12:39.759 --> 00:12:40.720
Mom and Dad couldn't bear to eat them,

00:12:40.799 --> 00:12:41.840
They saved them specially for the kids.

00:12:47.600 --> 00:12:48.559
I anticipated your anticipation

00:12:49.080 --> 00:12:49.960
Come on, brother. Sit here.

00:12:50.159 --> 00:12:50.639
Let's switch.

00:12:52.679 --> 00:12:53.039
Here, you sit.

00:12:53.279 --> 00:12:53.759
Here, eat up.

00:12:53.759 --> 00:12:54.440
Come on, eat more. You guys eat more.

00:12:54.440 --> 00:12:55.240
Just eat, hurry.

00:12:55.240 --> 00:12:56.080
Have some bean curd puffs.

00:12:57.000 --> 00:12:57.399
Come on.

00:12:57.799 --> 00:12:58.399
Come on, eat up.

00:12:58.600 --> 00:12:59.559
I beg you, just eat.

00:12:59.639 --> 00:13:00.399
This is my bowl, thanks.

00:13:00.840 --> 00:13:01.720
I want duck intestines.

00:13:02.000 --> 00:13:02.960
Here, give it to me.

00:13:03.200 --> 00:13:03.879
Here, Brother Li Wai.

00:13:07.360 --> 00:13:08.639
There you go.

00:13:11.279 --> 00:13:12.120
Which side is the front?

00:13:13.039 --> 00:13:13.519
Let me see.

00:13:14.440 --> 00:13:15.519
Like this, like this, like this.

00:13:15.840 --> 00:13:17.039
Put this underneath first.

00:13:22.679 --> 00:13:24.279
It's not done yet. Take off your shoes.

00:13:25.200 --> 00:13:26.360
Gui Fang, let me help you.

00:13:26.519 --> 00:13:27.279
Coming.

00:13:28.240 --> 00:13:28.879
Fly!

00:13:29.480 --> 00:13:30.440
I'm flying!

00:13:30.519 --> 00:13:31.080
Xiaocan.

00:13:31.240 --> 00:13:32.399
Come on, Xiaocan.

00:13:32.840 --> 00:13:33.519
Kong Xiaocan.

00:14:06.960 --> 00:14:07.720
Stop it, stop it.

00:14:07.720 --> 00:14:08.360
Let's go wash up.

00:14:09.000 --> 00:14:09.960
Alright, stop fighting. Go to sleep early.

00:14:10.159 --> 00:14:10.600
Brother.

00:14:10.720 --> 00:14:12.000
Your second wish came true, didn't it?

00:14:12.000 --> 00:14:13.600
You made this mess and just left it?

00:14:13.919 --> 00:14:15.039
You guys are unbelievable.

00:14:15.279 --> 00:14:16.759
No thanks, I'm on a diet.

00:14:16.759 --> 00:14:17.399
I'll drink plain water.

00:14:17.399 --> 00:14:18.759
Then I won't bother either. Let's go. I'm leaving.

00:14:19.080 --> 00:14:19.519
Gui Fang.

00:14:23.879 --> 00:14:24.159
You...

00:14:44.399 --> 00:14:46.159
This is what I originally looked like.

00:14:54.679 --> 00:14:56.120
My mom can't accept that I did a Life exchange for her.

00:14:56.600 --> 00:14:57.320
She will grow old.

00:14:57.440 --> 00:14:58.559
The Life Energy will be useless.

00:15:04.399 --> 00:15:05.000
It's okay.

00:15:06.480 --> 00:15:07.399
Everyone grows old.

00:15:11.879 --> 00:15:13.000
The day your age was exposed...

00:15:14.399 --> 00:15:15.519
I happened to pull an all-nighter.

00:15:16.679 --> 00:15:17.720
I was feeling totally groggy.

00:15:19.240 --> 00:15:20.000
As soon as I got home...

00:15:20.679 --> 00:15:21.960
I happened to run into a power outage.

00:15:22.759 --> 00:15:24.399
Then I saw you shining a flashlight on your face.

00:15:25.080 --> 00:15:25.879
Fixing the circuit breaker there.

00:15:28.799 --> 00:15:29.720
I thought I saw a ghost.

00:15:32.279 --> 00:15:33.360
I remember now.

