But when summer comes...

00:16:01.080 --> 00:16:02.320
Many wildflowers grow from the soil.

00:16:02.919 --> 00:16:03.639
They are colorful.

00:16:04.320 --> 00:16:05.799
Although I don't know their names...

00:16:06.240 --> 00:16:07.279
They only exist in my hometown.

00:16:08.240 --> 00:16:09.200
The sheep love eating them too.

00:16:12.200 --> 00:16:12.879
There will be a chance.

00:16:13.480 --> 00:16:13.919
Gui Fang.

00:16:19.000 --> 00:16:19.600
You must come.

00:16:24.320 --> 00:16:24.919
Go to sleep now.

