00:16:36.600 --> 00:16:38.039
You can't let the fifty years of life he gave...

00:16:38.759 --> 00:16:40.080
Only be exchanged for three years of your youth.

00:16:52.120 --> 00:16:52.759
You're right.

00:16:55.120 --> 00:16:55.960
I have to live well.

00:17:35.119 --> 00:17:36.480
Touch the hair, no fear. Touch the hair, no fear.

00:17:37.720 --> 00:17:39.279
Buddy, aren't you playing ghost a bit too early?

00:17:41.160 --> 00:17:42.480
Why sleep so much while alive?

00:17:43.079 --> 00:17:44.640
Death is an eternal sleep.

00:17:45.240 --> 00:17:46.160
I want to look at you guys more.

00:17:46.720 --> 00:17:47.640
You seem sick in the head.

00:17:47.640 --> 00:17:49.000
I'm really done with you.

00:17:54.359 --> 00:17:54.759
Brother.

00:17:56.519 --> 00:17:57.319
