00:17:58.319 --> 00:17:59.880
Don't you dare stand by my bed in the middle of the night.

00:18:06.240 --> 00:18:07.279
Come look at tombstones with me.

00:18:10.160 --> 00:18:10.559
Okay.

00:18:40.559 --> 00:18:41.200
Kong Xiaocan

00:18:41.759 --> 00:18:42.400
What time is it?

00:18:42.799 --> 00:18:43.559
Are you coming home or not?

00:18:44.200 --> 00:18:45.039
Are you going to eat or not?

00:18:45.160 --> 00:18:45.880
It's dinner time.

00:18:47.119 --> 00:18:48.319
Li Wai, come along too.

00:18:48.599 --> 00:18:49.680
Come eat at Auntie's house.

00:18:50.160 --> 00:18:50.920
Thank you, Auntie.

00:18:51.079 --> 00:18:52.559
Don't call me Auntie. Call me Godmother.

00:18:53.920 --> 00:18:54.359
Godmother.

00:18:55.400 --> 00:18:56.440
Come on, come down.

00:18:57.000 --> 00:18:58.519
Kong Xiaocan, why are your pants dirty again?

00:18:59.400 --> 00:19:00.079
Slow down, slow down.

00:19:00.079 --> 00:19:01.039
Li Wai, run slower.

00:19:05.079 --> 00:19:05.640
Mom.

00:19:06.079 --> 00:19:07.319
I broke the vase.

00:19:08.160 --> 00:19:10.240
Godmother, I broke the vase.

00:19:10.799 --> 00:19:11.559
I broke it.

00:19:12.000 --> 00:19:12.880
I broke it.

00:19:12.960 --> 00:19:13.839
It was me who broke it.

00:19:14.079 --> 00:19:15.160
It was me who broke it.

00:19:15.160 --> 00:19:16.319
You've grown up.

00:19:17.200 --> 00:19:18.039
You're taking responsibility.

00:19:18.599 --> 00:19:20.359
Does that mean we won't get a beating?

00:19:22.279 --> 00:19:23.200
What do you think?

00:19:23.599 --> 00:19:24.519
Haven't I told you?

00:19:24.960 --> 00:19:26.680
That the flower pots on the balcony are off-limits?

00:19:27.359 --> 00:19:27.960
Li Wai didn't know.

00:19:27.960 --> 00:19:28.759
You didn't know?

00:19:29.079 --> 00:19:30.039
You used to be so obedient.

00:19:30.039 --> 00:19:31.559
Didn't Godmother say you couldn't?

00:19:32.599 --> 00:19:34.039
Kong Xiaocan led you astray, didn't he?

00:19:34.599 --> 00:19:35.759
Learning this stuff from Kong Xiaocan.

00:19:36.720 --> 00:19:37.720
Brother, brother, don't be nervous.

00:19:38.000 --> 00:19:39.000
Hold her favorite thing,

00:19:39.000 --> 00:19:40.400
and say the words "I like you."

00:19:40.680 --> 00:19:41.839
Don't be nervous. You got this.

00:19:42.000 --> 00:19:42.720
No. Come on. Get ready.

00:19:47.480 --> 00:19:48.039
Say it!

00:19:48.720 --> 00:19:49.160
Say it.

00:19:55.279 --> 00:19:55.880
Happy Mid-Autumn Festival.

00:19:59.119 --> 00:20:00.160
He likes you.

00:20:31.559 --> 00:20:32.039
You're awake.

00:20:33.960 --> 00:20:34.799
You're awake. Oh my god.

00:20:34.799 --> 00:20:35.799
You slept for quite a long time.

00:20:36.200 --> 00:20:36.720
Where is everyone?

00:20:37.839 --> 00:20:38.400
Godmother and the others?

00:20:38.680 --> 00:20:39.599
They went to tidy up the new house.

00:20:41.759 --> 00:20:42.279
Where did they go?

00:20:42.480 --> 00:20:43.519
They went to tidy up the new house.

00:20:44.640 --> 00:20:45.119
Where?

00:20:46.640 --> 00:20:47.799
To tidy up the new house, grandpa.

00:20:47.920 --> 00:20:49.119
How come your ears aren't working?

00:20:52.880 --> 00:20:53.480
No.

