00:24:27.119 --> 00:24:27.640
Me.

00:24:36.279 --> 00:24:36.799
Thanks.

00:24:38.000 --> 00:24:38.559
And me.

00:24:42.960 --> 00:24:44.519
Thanks to you too. Thanks.

00:24:44.920 --> 00:24:45.680
Actually, it was me.

00:25:00.920 --> 00:25:01.480
I don't mind.

00:25:04.279 --> 00:25:04.880
In fact,

00:25:06.000 --> 00:25:06.599
I like you too.

00:25:09.880 --> 00:25:11.640
Since it's rare for us all to be together,

00:25:12.039 --> 00:25:12.880
