00:25:13.240 --> 00:25:13.880
You choose.

00:25:14.240 --> 00:25:15.519
Which type do you actually like? Okay?

00:25:15.519 --> 00:25:16.160
Let's go, let's go, Xiaocan.

00:25:16.160 --> 00:25:16.880
Let's go, let's go.

00:25:17.039 --> 00:25:17.640
Come on.

00:25:18.200 --> 00:25:19.200
None of us are the same type.

00:25:19.279 --> 00:25:20.720
No rush. Let's eat.

00:25:21.079 --> 00:25:21.680
There's definitely something wrong.

00:25:22.160 --> 00:25:22.640
Brother.

00:25:23.000 --> 00:25:24.039
Can, Can, Can.

00:25:24.880 --> 00:25:25.480
Don't be in a rush.

