00:25:39.240 --> 00:25:39.640
Not to die.

00:25:40.640 --> 00:25:41.480
Let me ask you this way.

00:25:41.720 --> 00:25:43.319
If we held a ceremony for you right now,

00:25:43.799 --> 00:25:46.480
what would you want it to be?

00:25:47.960 --> 00:25:48.440
Don't think.

00:25:49.000 --> 00:25:49.519
Don't think.

00:26:13.599 --> 00:26:14.200
Xiaocan.

00:26:25.279 --> 00:26:26.640
I should have known.

00:26:27.200 --> 00:26:28.079
I told you,

00:26:28.079 --> 00:26:29.839
I don't want a living funeral.

00:26:29.920 --> 00:26:30.880
I don't want a living funeral.

00:26:30.880 --> 00:26:32.279
Why can't you just listen to me?

00:26:32.359 --> 00:26:33.279
I'm afraid of upsetting my mom.

00:26:33.279 --> 00:26:34.039
No, when she saw it...

00:26:35.319 --> 00:26:36.079
Did she get upset?

00:26:36.240 --> 00:26:36.799
No, brother.

00:26:38.079 --> 00:26:38.519
Mom.

00:26:39.000 --> 00:26:39.440
Mom.

00:26:39.640 --> 00:26:39.880
Mom.

00:27:57.079 --> 00:27:57.920
Thank you, Auntie

