00:30:15.079 --> 00:30:17.200
hobbies I love and excel at

00:30:17.920 --> 00:30:18.799
and a group of

00:30:19.119 --> 00:30:19.799
friends who understand

00:30:20.279 --> 00:30:21.640
and support me

00:30:23.240 --> 00:30:24.319
I never felt

00:30:24.920 --> 00:30:25.640
that I lacked anything

00:30:26.880 --> 00:30:27.559
Love

00:30:28.559 --> 00:30:29.359
is merely

00:30:30.160 --> 00:30:31.279
a rose on the sword

00:30:32.359 --> 00:30:34.240
I just want to be the fastest knight

00:30:36.640 --> 00:30:37.400
But then

00:30:39.519 --> 00:30:41.160
I met another knight

00:30:43.839 --> 00:30:45.920
Although he is childish and impulsive

00:30:46.799 --> 00:30:47.480
and

00:30:47.640 --> 00:30:49.519
gets lost in his own greatness

00:30:51.720 --> 00:30:52.759
but at the same time

00:30:53.599 --> 00:30:54.640
he has a kind heart

00:30:55.960 --> 00:30:58.000
and courage beyond anyone else's

00:30:59.599 --> 00:31:00.440
I am very proud

00:31:01.839 --> 00:31:03.039
to be in love with such a

00:31:03.799 --> 00:31:05.640
knight who dares to sacrifice

00:31:10.640 --> 00:31:11.240
Kong Xiaocan

00:31:15.279 --> 00:31:16.000
are you willing

00:31:16.920 --> 00:31:18.039
to become my husband?

00:31:25.920 --> 00:31:26.400
I do

00:32:11.759 --> 00:32:12.359
Do you remember?

00:32:40.440 --> 00:32:40.920
Xu Rui

00:32:44.119 --> 00:32:44.759
Thank you.

00:32:45.599 --> 00:32:46.319
For always

00:32:47.240 --> 00:32:48.039
understanding me,

00:32:49.279 --> 00:32:50.000
tolerating me,

00:32:50.799 --> 00:32:52.400
and when I faced such a special situation,

00:32:53.880 --> 00:32:55.119
for staying by my side to face it.

00:32:57.319 --> 00:32:58.720
In the past, I...

00:33:00.119 --> 00:33:00.880
I even felt

00:33:02.519 --> 00:33:03.759
all of this was unreal.

00:33:05.319 --> 00:33:07.160
How could I have such a perfect girlfriend?

00:33:11.200 --> 00:33:11.880
To be honest,

00:33:12.880 --> 00:33:16.039
I've fantasized about this scene countless times.

00:33:17.720 --> 00:33:18.480
But...

00:33:24.039 --> 00:33:24.559
thank you.

00:33:30.759 --> 00:33:31.759
People always say,

00:33:32.759 --> 00:33:34.200
"Love only one person in a lifetime."

00:33:35.799 --> 00:33:37.000
I think I'm very lucky.

00:33:40.039 --> 00:33:41.279
In this life, I've only ever loved you.

00:33:43.279 --> 00:33:44.079
And I will love you forever.

00:33:49.960 --> 00:33:50.519
Lin Xurui,

00:33:52.160 --> 00:33:53.039
will you marry me?

00:34:00.279 --> 00:34:00.799
I will.

00:34:02.000 --> 00:34:02.400
Yes!

00:34:27.760 --> 00:34:28.199
Wait a second.

00:34:31.719 --> 00:34:32.559
Do you remember that?

00:34:47.320 --> 00:34:47.880
Kong Xiaocan,

00:34:52.159 --> 00:34:53.960
are you willing to keep this promise?

00:34:55.119 --> 00:34:55.639
Lin Xurui,

00:34:57.159 --> 00:34:58.159
in life, I am yours,

00:34:58.840 --> 00:34:59.679
and in death, I am your ghost.

00:36:51.920 --> 00:36:52.880
Let's go, let's go inside and play.

00:36:53.079 --> 00:36:53.559
Let's go, Fang'er.

00:36:55.880 --> 00:36:57.159
Godmother, let's go.

00:36:57.400 --> 00:36:58.760
Let's go inside for a drink, hurry.

00:36:59.440 --> 00:36:59.960
Coming.

00:37:00.760 --> 00:37:01.719
Wait for me.

00:37:01.920 --> 00:37:02.960
The big devil is coming.

00:37:41.079 --> 00:37:42.280
Godmother, come on!

00:38:03.119 --> 00:38:03.480
Fang'er!

00:38:04.880 --> 00:38:06.079
Let's go! What are you doing?

00:38:11.239 --> 00:38:12.239
It looks so good.

00:38:13.039 --> 00:38:14.280
So cute! Send it to me, send it to me.

00:38:14.280 --> 00:38:15.480
No. Beg me.

00:38:15.840 --> 00:38:16.679
I beg you.

00:38:17.039 --> 00:38:18.079
I'll send it to you. Come here.

00:39:00.719 --> 00:39:01.280
Bro.

00:39:04.280 --> 00:39:05.239
Let's go, bro.

00:39:05.320 --> 00:39:06.400
We're coming back in a bit.

00:39:22.199 --> 00:39:23.239
Let's head out in a little while.

00:39:23.440 --> 00:39:24.440
Let's not stay for dinner.

00:39:25.880 --> 00:39:26.840
We should give the mother and son

00:39:26.840 --> 00:39:28.039
some time alone together.

00:39:30.920 --> 00:39:31.800
Godmother looks good in these clothes.

00:39:32.239 --> 00:39:32.559
Tian'er.

00:39:35.480 --> 00:39:36.960
My mom actually likes...

00:39:39.599 --> 00:39:40.440
You know what she likes.

00:39:43.800 --> 00:39:44.519
Brother Xiao Can, where are you going?

00:39:46.920 --> 00:39:48.360
I heard there's popcorn for sale over there.

00:39:48.440 --> 00:39:49.239
I'll buy two bags of popcorn.

00:39:49.519 --> 00:39:50.559
It's "blossoming," so it's lucky.

00:39:51.159 --> 00:39:51.760
I'll go with you.

00:39:51.880 --> 00:39:52.840
No need. You guys go back first.

00:39:53.920 --> 00:39:54.679
Then we'll head out first.

00:39:54.760 --> 00:39:55.079
Let's go.

00:39:58.559 --> 00:40:01.239
Delicious popcorn for sale!

00:40:01.679 --> 00:40:03.760
Eight yuan a bag!

00:40:04.199 --> 00:40:06.360
Fifteen yuan for two bags!

00:40:07.199 --> 00:40:08.800
Scan to taste!

00:40:10.199 --> 00:40:12.559
Uncle, pop a fresh pot for me.

00:40:13.880 --> 00:40:14.639
Pop a pot?

00:40:16.440 --> 00:40:18.440
One pot. Scan to taste!

00:40:18.519 --> 00:40:18.800
Okay.

00:40:18.800 --> 00:40:21.199
I'll scan, scan. The freshly popped one, that one.

00:40:21.360 --> 00:40:21.719
One pot.

00:40:21.760 --> 00:40:22.440
Okay, alright.

00:40:22.440 --> 00:40:22.960
One pot, alright.

00:40:23.079 --> 00:40:23.400
Alright.

00:40:56.840 --> 00:40:57.559
Careful, careful.

00:41:00.079 --> 00:41:01.000
Let me help you carry a bag.

00:41:01.000 --> 00:41:01.480
No need, no need.

00:41:02.280 --> 00:41:02.760
Be careful.

00:41:44.440 --> 00:41:45.280
Young man,

00:41:45.760 --> 00:41:48.039
it's about to pop! Cover your ears!

00:41:48.039 --> 00:41:49.079
Okay, okay, okay.